{"id": "art-1442", "label": "Art. 1442", "title": "Art. 1442", "slug": "art-1442", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1653217868\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2180\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1653217868\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 144<sup>2</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_182409992\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2179\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_182409992\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Administratorii sunt r&#259;spunz&#259;tori de\nîndeplinirea tuturor <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iilor</span>, potrivit\nprevederilor art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>72</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>73</span><span style='color:black'>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1748553884\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2178\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1748553884\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Administratorii r&#259;spund <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span>\nde societate pentru prejudiciile cauzate prin actele îndeplinite de directori\nsau de personalul încadrat, când dauna nu s-ar fi produs dac&#259; ei ar fi\nexercitat supravegherea impus&#259; de îndatoririle <span class=SpellE>func&#355;iei</span>\nlor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_168857318\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2177\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_168857318\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Directorii vor <span class=SpellE>în&#351;tiin&#355;a</span>\nconsiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> de toate neregulile\nconstatate cu ocazia îndeplinirii <span class=SpellE>atribu&#355;iilor</span>\nlor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1848449409\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2176\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1848449409\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Administratorii sunt solidar r&#259;spunz&#259;tori cu\npredecesorii lor <span class=SpellE>imedia&#355;i</span> dac&#259;, având <span\nclass=SpellE>cuno&#351;tin&#355;&#259;</span> de neregulile <span class=SpellE>s&#259;vâr&#351;ite</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>ace&#351;tia</span>, nu le comunic&#259; cenzorilor sau,\ndup&#259; caz, auditorilor interni <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nauditorului financiar.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1671123545\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2175\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1671123545\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)În <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> care\nau mai <span class=SpellE>mul&#355;i</span> administratori r&#259;spunderea\npentru actele <span class=SpellE>s&#259;vâr&#351;ite</span> sau pentru omisiuni\nnu se întinde <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> la administratorii care au\nf&#259;cut s&#259; se consemneze, în registrul deciziilor consiliului de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, împotrivirea lor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nau <span class=SpellE>încuno&#351;tin&#355;at</span> despre aceasta, în scris,\npe cenzori sau auditorii interni <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> auditorul\nfinanciar.</span></p>"}